snippet.title: Power Supplied Trailer
snippet.description:
Power Supplied is a multiplayer puzzle game, a one-to-four player game where four characters are controlled, each with different methods of traversing levels. Constantly changing routes will mean passing over the same ground many times to try and reach your freedom. 
Steam Page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/755760/Power_Supplied/
King's Lance Games website: http://www.kingslancegames.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/KingsLanceGames
